table_trans: Government Order No: MVD 0923 / PRQ र.319/पर G-4
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,
Appointment of transfers and discharge of government duties of Maharashtra Government employees.
Pursuant to the provisions of Sections 4 (4) (2) and 4 (5) of the Prevention of Delay Act, 2005
Regional Transport Officer cadre with the approval of the authority competent to make the transfer.
Transfer of officers to the post indicated in column No.4 in front of their names on their request.
The concerned Controlling Officer shall transfer the said transferred officers to their present place of posting.
Removal from office with immediate effect and posting of officers concerned at the place of new posting.
Report submitted to the Government by the Transport Commissioner's Office of joining and assuming office within the period
The Government Order is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
It has been coded as 2024090313499929. The order is digitally signed.
By order and in the name of the Governor of Maharashtra.
Secretary to the Hon'ble Governor, Raj Bhavan, Mumbai
Additional Chief Secretary to the Chief Minister, Mantralaya, Mumbai
Commissioner of Transport, Maharashtra State, Mumbai
Accountant General, (Accounts & Licensure) Maharashtra 1⁄2, Mumbai / Nagpur
Shri Vijay Ramsinh Chavan, Regional Transport Officer (through Transport Commissioner)
